title: ↪ 📱 * Live Limitlessly In This 2/2 Furnished BRICKELL: Dont Wait Any Longer
posting_body: ['REF# 10R26', '$4200 · 2/2 · Furnished · 1117 Sqft · Brickell · Brickell On The River N T', 'Call ➟ Text ➟ WhatsApp', "📲 786'*'5O5'*'4314", 'Carlos Manchego', 'Goldstein Realty', 'show contact info', '* LIVE LIMITLESSLY in this turn-key bright and spacious 2/2 corner unit offering a versatile living space w/ both bedrooms in separate wings for privacy.', 'If you like to cook, you’ll love this kitchen with ample counter space & storage.', 'The master bedroom is equipped w/ a ceiling fan, built-out closet, master bathroom with double sinks & a private balcony.', 'The unit’s 2 balconies boast gorgeous views of the Miami River, Biscayne Bay and Downtown.', 'Situated on the riverfront, BOR is just steps from Brickell’s world-class shopping, luxury dining, and premium entertainment.', 'Exit the property to the 5th ST metro-mover station, where you can hop on the mover for convenient free transport anywhere in Brickell/Downtown.', 'Building amenities include 2 pools, 4 story gym, business center, and clubroom.', 'Read Less', 'REF# 10R26', 'tags:', 'holleman park homes, baltus house, tequesta point condos, four seasons residences, the loft ii, 50 biscayne, baltus house, tequesta point condos, one paraiso, quantum on the bay, virginia pointe condo, blue condo, midtown, jade brickell, the bond, the loft 1 downtown, the loft downtown i, brickell city centre - condo west, vizcayne, marina blue, venetia condo, brickell biscayne, the crimson, pet-friendly rentals, biscayne 21, mint condo, the crimson, opera tower, paraiso bay condo, ion east edgewater, residences at vizcaya, lofts in the grove,, hyde midtown, icon brickell', '_mr10']
